/*
 * Brief of Drinkbot
 *
 * State Machine:
 *
 *                   BOOTING
 *                      |
 *                      v
 *   (collect data) LISTENING <-+
 *        API called? Y |       |
 *                      v       |
 *                    START     |
 *                      |       | finished? Y
 *                      v       |
 *              +--> PUMPING    |
 *  finished? N |       |       |
 *              +-------+-------+
 *                      |
 *                      v
 *                     end (never reach here)
 */

